	sum += @Total_Deductions.ScheduleVIA.Sec80GGA.Schedule80GGACust.Schedule80GGATable.DonationDtlsSciRsrchRuralDev[i]Grp2.DonationAmtCash
}

sum += @Total_Deductions.ScheduleVIA.Sec80GGA.Schedule80GGACust.Schedule80GGATable.DonationDtlsSciRsrchRuralDev[i]Grp2.DonationAmtOtherMode
sum = Min(sum, @Gross_Total_Income.ITR1_IncomeDeductions.Group.GrossTotIncome)
return sum
